### 2. Get All DBlockers
GET {{host}}/api/dblockers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get DBlocker by ID
GET {{host}}/api/dblockers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update DBlocker by ID
PUT {{host}}/api/dblockers/14
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "5 Terminal Utama Tsingsan",
    "serial_numb": "250005",
    "ip": "10.88.81.6",
    "latitude": -2.808731,
    "longitude": 122.147636,
    "desc": "Blocker 5 Terminal Utama Tsingsan",
    "angle_start": 0
}


### 5. Delete DBlocker by ID
DELETE {{host}}/api/dblockers/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 6. Update DBlocker Config
PUT {{host}}/api/dblockers/config
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "id": 6,
    "config": [
        {"signal_ctrl": true, "signal_gps": false},
        {"signal_ctrl": true, "signal_gps": false},
        {"signal_ctrl": true, "signal_gps": false},
        {"signal_ctrl": false, "signal_gps": true},
        {"signal_ctrl": false, "signal_gps": true},
        {"signal_ctrl": false, "signal_gps": true}
    ]
}

### 7. Turn Off All DBlocker Config
GET {{host}}/api/dblockers/config/off/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7b. Turn Off All DBlocker Config B
GET {{host}}/api/dblockers/config/off/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Save Preset Config (store preset ON state for a dblocker)
PUT {{host}}/api/dblockers/preset
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "id": 6,
    "config": [
        {"signal_ctrl": true, "signal_gps": false},
        {"signal_ctrl": true, "signal_gps": false},
        {"signal_ctrl": true, "signal_gps": false},
        {"signal_ctrl": false, "signal_gps": true},
        {"signal_ctrl": false, "signal_gps": true},
        {"signal_ctrl": false, "signal_gps": true}
    ]
}

### 9. Apply Preset ON (publish saved preset config to device via MQTT)
GET {{host}}/api/dblockers/config/preset/6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}